# Portfolio Workflow

## Target Repository

- **Always** apply all changes to the main Portfolio repo: `/Users/mojtabatorabi/Desktop/Portfolio`
- **Never** apply changes to other locations (e.g. Portfolio-live-repo or other clones)
- The main repo is published at: https://github.com/mojitorabi/Portfolio

## After Every Change

1. Stage all modified and new files
2. Commit with a clear message describing the changes
3. Push to the remote `origin` on branch `main`

## Git Commands to Run After Edits

```bash
cd /Users/mojtabatorabi/Desktop/Portfolio
git add -A
git status  # verify before commit
git commit -m "Descriptive message"
git push origin main
```

## Exclusions

- Do not commit: `.venv/`, `.DS_Store`, `.env`, `*.pdf` (unless explicitly needed)
- Respect `.gitignore` when staging
